            </div>
        </div>
        <section class="call_to_action">
            <h5 class="section_header fancy centered">
                We are able to provide all kind of food, drinks and snacks. Send a <a href='@Url.Action("ContactUs", "Engelsk")'>message</a> and we will make it for you!
